### Test API Endpoints for Job Management

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### Execute Command (Creates Job Entry)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/commands/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "ls -la /tmp"
}

### Execute Another Command
POST http://localhost:3000/api/commands/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "echo 'Hello World from remote server'"
}

### Execute Long Running Command
POST http://localhost:3000/api/commands/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "sleep 10 && echo 'Completed after 10 seconds'"
}

### Get All Jobs
GET http://localhost:3000/api/jobs

### Get Jobs with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/api/jobs?limit=2&offset=0

### Get Jobs by Status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/jobs?status=failed

